n, Polish, Russian, Arabic, and others!       Film Series  LCLC hosts Film Series in different languages and programs. Click here to find out what film series are currently offered and when they are happening!       Special Events  LCLC also hosts special events in the Language Oasis. See here for more details and the current schedule.         What's happening at LCLC     What's happening at LCLC            Events    Back to main content           Schedule of Events    Conversation Hours     Arabic Conversation Hour    Chinese Conversation Hour    French Conversation Hour    German Conversation Hour (SprachCafe)    Italian Conversation Hour (Piazza Italia)    Japanese Conversation Hour    Spanish Conversation Hour      Film Series     Ancient World, Modern Media    Central & Eastern European Film Club      Special Events             Reserve the Language Oasis  If you would like to schedule a special event in our Language Oasis please click here and let us know how we can help.      Today's Events  See what Conversations Hours, Film Series, and special events are happening today in GH 308!      Peer Tutoring  Find out more about our Peer Tutoring program, meet the tutors, and view schedules for Spanish, Italian, French, and German Peer Tutoring in GH 305 & GH 308!      School of Literatures, Cultural Studies and Linguistics  The School of Literatures, Cultural Studies and Linguistics (LCSL) is home to six independent departments, three academic programs, and the Sandi Port Errant Language and Culture Learning Center.                  UIC Logo         Language  And Culture  Learning Center  College of  Liberal Arts  And  Sciences         Contact   Language and Culture Learning Center  703 South Morgan St., 301 GH Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996 2119  lclc@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information 